{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji22.pdf"],"article":{"title":"确有把握方可攻击瓦究堡或婚龙","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"确有把握方可攻击瓦窑堡或蟠龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年4月30日）彭、习："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过精密之侦察，确有把握，方可下决心攻击瓦窑堡或蟠龙，如无充分把握，以不打为宜，部队加紧休整，以逸待劳，准备运动中歼敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军委"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卯三十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给西北野战兵团司令员兼政治委员彭德怀和副政治委员习仲勋的电报。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":4,"day":30}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":543,"page_end":543},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}